groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:name: Spirit Quest: Spirits of The Past
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:short_description:
A quiet placed tucked away but very close to the path way. It is actually on the Cross Island Trail.

The park is open from sunup to sundown. Pets are allowed but must be leashed.
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:long_description:
During the summer months this little place is somewhat more concealed but if you follow the trail when you get close you should be able to find your way in with little to no problems.


The WP's will be more for reference than anything else.



Proud member of the Military Association of GeoCachers



*****Good Job on FTF Corfmania*****
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:encoded_hints: Only remove the container & not the holder.

groundspeak:log.groundspeak:text: Found this one after walking around the cross island trail. Lots of bugs, a few deer and a fox, along with a number of cool birds. Found with dawnie22.
